  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Optimization was performed using AdamW with a learning rate of 4 × 10 -5, 10% linear warmup, and weight decay of 0.05.",
    "We evaluated model performance every 50 steps on a held-out validation set, which consisted of the last 30% of the development dataset.",
    "The development set includes 300 dialogues sourced from the MathDial (Macina et al., 2023) and Bridge (Wang et al., 2024) datasets.Checkpoints were saved every 100 steps with a retention window of the three most recent.",
    "Only LoRA adapter weights were saved to minimize disk usage and enable efficient inference.",
    "All training runs were conducted in a single-node setup with world_size=1."
  ],
